-- Oman to Sign Tight Gas Deal With BP by September, Observer Says
-- B y   A y e s h a   D a y a
-- 2012-07-22T09:29:45Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-07-22/oman-to-sign-tight-gas-deal-with-bp-by-september-observer-says.html
BP Plc (BP/)  plans to sign a heads of
agreement for Oman’s Block 61 natural-gas area by September, the
 Oman Daily Observer  reported, citing an adviser to the country’s
oil and gas ministry.  Negotiations are progressing well on a so-called tight gas
project in the Khazzan-Makarem field to ensure production starts
at the end of 2016, Shaikh Ali bin Thabit al-Battashi said,
according to the newspaper.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Ayesha Daya in Dubai at 
 adaya1@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
